Lines: Friendly spec-ops attacked this base recently.
On that occasion, they decimated local garrison.
Naturally, the Federation should be reinforcing
this base, but for such remote location
it will take some time.
However, if they get word out that shuttle
has been stolen, we'll be intercepted in orbit.
We must prioritize destruction of thier comms.
Correct. Demolish communication facility.
Secure the shuttle and destory garrison.
Leave nothing to chance in our return to space.
Space...
I haven't been on Earth that long,
but I miss home.
Me too...
We all want to get back, it all rests
on our backs.
Right. Let's do it, Leo.
Give it all you got... to the end!
That's right! We wont hold back!
We'll do everything we can to complete
this mission!
Brauer's Squad, let's go!
Roger that!
